IEL Robot Simulator

Install Guide
-----------------------------------------------------------
The robot simulator has three libraries:
	1) crobosim library
	2) opende library
	3) tinyxml2 library
2 and 3 must be compiled before 1.  OpenSceneGraph is used
for graphics.  It must be installed into the system before
compiling.

See below for instructions on how to build each one.

Linux
-----------------------------------------------------------

tinyxml2
-----------------------------
	cd src/tinyxml2/
	cmake .
	make
	cd ../../

opende
-----------------------------
	cd src/opende/
	sh autogen.sh
	./configure --prefix=$PWD"/sys/" --enable-double-precision --enable-shared --enable-static --disable-demos --with-trimesh=none --with-drawstuff=none
	make
	make install
	cd ../../

crobotsim
-----------------------------
	cd src/crobotsim/
	cmake .
	make
	cd ../../

demos
-----------------------------
Each demo can be compiled separately by invoking
make <name>
	cd demos/
	cmake .
	make <name>
	cd ../

chrobotsim
-----------------------------
	cd src/chrobotsim/
	make
	make createpkg
	cd chrobotsim*/
	sudo make install
	cd ../../../

